ue. We understand that each customer is different.\r\n\r\n[/kc_column_text][/kc_column_inner][kc_column_inner width=\"33.33%\" _id=\"950531\"][kc_icon _id=\"822633\" icon=\"sl-like\"][kc_title text=\"Tm8gSGlkZGVuIEZlZXM=\" _id=\"450885\" type=\"h3\"][kc_column_text _id=\"256917\"]\r\n\r\nHonest, upfront pricing with no surprises. No excess usage charges. No credit card fees. What you see is what you get.\r\n\r\n[/kc_column_text][/kc_column_inner][kc_column_inner width=\"33.33%\" _id=\"2077\"][kc_icon _id=\"589325\" icon=\"sl-login\"][kc_title text=\"RmxleGlibGUgT3B0aW9ucw==\" _id=\"221418\" type=\"h3\"][kc_column_text _id=\"783094\"]\r\n\r\nWe have no Lock In Contracts. Choose from our range of generous plans and we won’t lock you in to any fixed terms. Its very flexible.\r\n\r\n[/kc_column_text][/kc_column_inner][/kc_row_inner][kc_row_inner column_align=\"middle\" _id=\"825477\"][kc_column_inner width=\"100%\" _id=\"595029\"][kc_spacing height=\"30px\" _id=\"273316\"][/kc_column_inner][/kc_row_inner][kc_row_inner column_align=\"middle\" _id=\"569902\"][kc_column_inner width=\"33.33%\" _id=\"402376\"][kc_icon _id=\"815160\" icon=\"sl-screen-desktop\"][kc_title text=\"TkJOIE9OTFk=\" _id=\"95208\" type=\"h3\"][kc_column_text _id=\"318975\"]\r\n\r\nOur data plans are 100% delivered on the NBN without the distraction of competing products. Unlike other Telco’s we won’t bundle in products that you don’t want or need.\r\n\r\n[/kc_column_text][/kc_column_inner][kc_column_inner width=\"33.33%\" _id=\"935386\"][kc_icon _id=\"764713\" icon=\"sl-screen-smartphone\"][kc_title text=\"QllPIE1vYmlsZSA=\" _id=\"669410\" type=\"h3\"][kc_column_text _id=\"941829\"]\r\n\r\nAt BroadSignal we can provide mobile plans using the Telstra Network with no Lock in Contracts and competitive pricing.\r\n\r\n[/kc_column_text][/kc_column_inner][kc_column_inner width=\"33.33%\" _id=\"599954\"][kc_icon _id=\"387532\" icon=\"sl-people\"][kc_title text=\"T25lIEJpbGwgT25seQ==\" _id=\"415147\" type=\"h