d Definition\r\n\r\nIf you\'re streaming on high (or auto), watching a season of your favourite show on Netflix (13 episodes) could use as much as 39GB.\r\n\r\nStan       Approx. 570MB in Standard Definition\r\n\r\nWatching a season of your favourite show on Stan (13 episodes) on high will use about 37GB.\r\n\r\nSource: www.whistleout.com.au/Broadband/Guides/Broadband-Usage-Guide\r\n\r\n[/kc_column_text][/kc_accordion_tab][/kc_accordion][/kc_column][/kc_row]','FAQ','','inherit','closed','closed','','435-revision-v1','','','2017-11-01 07:25:44','2017-11-01 07:25:44','',435,'http://demo.broadsignal.com.au/?p=529',0,'revision','',0),(530,2,'2017-11-01 07:58:22','2017-11-01 07:58:22','','Login','','inherit','closed','closed','','32-revision-v1','','','2017-11-01 07:58:22','2017-11-01 07:58:22','',32,'http://demo.broadsignal.com.au/?p=530',0,'revision','',0),(531,2,'2017-11-01 08:38:59','2017-11-01 08:38:59','[kc_row][kc_column width=\"12/12\" video_mute=\"no\" _id=\"42581\"][kc_icon _id=\"861717\" icon=\"sl-user\"][kc_icon _id=\"733926\" icon=\"et-profile-male\"][/kc_column][/kc_row]','Login','','inherit','closed','closed','','32-revision-v1','','','2017-11-01 08:38:59','2017-11-01 08:38:59','',32,'http://demo.broadsignal.com.au/?p=531',0,'revision','',0),(532,2,'2017-11-01 08:46:22','2017-11-01 08:46:22','','Login','','inherit','closed','closed','','32-revision-v1','','','2017-11-01 08:46:22','2017-11-01 08:46:22','',32,'http://demo.broadsignal.com.au/?p=532',0,'revision','',0),(533,2,'2017-11-02 00:32:12','2017-11-02 00:32:12','','image002','','inherit','open','closed','','image002','','','2017-11-02 00:32:39','2017-11-02 00:32:39','',229,'http://demo.broadsignal.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/image002.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(534,2,'2017-11-02 00:33:12','2017-11-02 00:33:12','<img class=\"wp-image-533 alignright\" src=\"http://demo.broadsignal.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/image002.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"467\" height=\"613\" />In 1870 the Overland 